'''Tasekla''' yekka-d seg wawal [[asekkil]] (tira umesli aḥerfi), d ayen yaɛnan [[tira]], [[tajerrumt]], [[idles]], atg.
D tajruma n idrisen, neɣ n wayen yakw yettwaqedcen ama s wudem n tira neɣ s win n watlay. Tasekla tamawit ar yezwawen, wala ar imaziɣen s umata, teǧhed. Ma d tasekla n tira, armi d timdi aki taneggarut i bdan a ttarun. 

== Gret Tamawt ==
Wagi d amuɣ kan amezwaru, yal win isɛan akud, ad ikemel amuɣ-agi n imyura izwawen 
iwakken aten-id-adden akken ma llan.

